      "text": "ERCOT Wind Farm Map & Project List\n\nERCOT Wind Farm Map &amp; Project List\n[![Cleanview logo](https://cleanview.co/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Flogo%2Fcleanview_orange_sun_logo.png&w=64&q=75&dpl=dpl_6acS6XhD8ao9twBxLZQ91URkptGy)Cleanview](https://cleanview.co/)\n[Sign In](https://cleanview.co/login)[Start Free Trial](https://cleanview.co/signup)\n# Wind Farms in ERCOT\nExplore the largest wind farms in ERCOT and see all the utility-scale wind projects in ERCOT on a map.\nLast updated: May 2026\nOn this page, you can explore our **real-time database of wind farms in ERCOT.** Each month, we track wind projects and update our list of the largest wind farms in ERCOT.\nAs of May 2026, there are **198 utility-scale wind farms** in ERCOT, according to [Cleanview's project tracker](https://cleanview.co/). Their total operating capacity is 40,234 MW. In 2025, there were **8** wind farms built in ERCOT. See also: [planned wind farms in ERCOT→](https://cleanview.co/power-projects/planned/wind-farms/ercot)\nTotal Wind Farms\n198\nTotal Capacity\n40,234 MW\nBuilt in 2025\n8\n## ERCOT Wind Map\nMap of wind farms in ERCOT. Marker size reflects capacity — only facilities with reported capacity data are shown.\n## Largest Wind Farms in ERCOT\n[\n### Horse Hollow Wind Energy Center\n736 MW\nYear Operational: June 2006\nLocation: Taylor, Texas\n](https://cleanview.co/power-projects/operating/wind-farms/ercot/56291/horse-hollow-wind-energy-center)[\n### Capricorn Ridge Wind LLC\n663 MW\nYear Operational: May 2008\nLocation: Sterling, Texas\n](https://cleanview.co/power-projects/operating/wind-farms/ercot/56763/capricorn-ridge-wind-llc)[\n### Aviator Wind\n525 MW\nYear Operational: June 2021\nLocation: Coke, Texas\n](https://cleanview.co/power-projects/operating/wind-farms/ercot/63209/aviator-wind)[\n### White Mesa Wind\n501 MW\nYear Operational: October 2021\nLocation: Crockett, Texas\n](https://cleanview.co/power-projects/operating/wind-farms/ercot/64710/white-mesa-wi